cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.NE, cs.SI

This paper proposes a new classification method based on the rough set theory and extreme learning machine. It focuses on improving the accuracy and repeatability of classification tasks for high-dimensional data. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DM (Data Mining). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which suggests the possibility of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
